## {{ package_slug }}.core — 核心模块

### 常量

```python
PACKAGE_NAME = "{{ package_slug }}"
PROJECT_NAME = "{{ project_slug }}"
PROJECT_DESC = "{{ project_description }}"
PROJECT_VERSION: str                    # 从 pyproject.toml 动态读取
DEFAULT_CONFIG_PATH: Path               # 用户配置目录下的默认路径
```

### 枚举

```python
class EnvironmentType(StrEnum):
    DEVELOPMENT = "development"
    STAGING    = "staging"
    PRODUCTION = "production"
    TESTING    = "testing"

class LogLevel(StrEnum):
    DEBUG    = "DEBUG"
    INFO     = "INFO"
    WARNING  = "WARNING"
    ERROR    = "ERROR"
    CRITICAL = "CRITICAL"

class DatabaseType(StrEnum):
    POSTGRESQL = "postgresql"
    MYSQL      = "mysql"
    SQLITE     = "sqlite"

class ConfigType(StrEnum):
    TOML = "toml"
    YAML = "yaml"
    ENV  = "ENV"
```

### 函数

```python
def get_project_version(project_name: str = PROJECT_NAME) -> str
    """从 pyproject.toml 动态读取版本, 失败时回退到内置 __version__"""

def get_default_config_path(config_type: str = "toml") -> Path
    """返回平台特定的默认配置文件路径 (通过 platformdirs)"""
```

### 装饰器

```python
@log_command(cmd_name: str)
    """命令日志装饰器, 记录命令名称和参数"""
    # 用法: @log_command("fetch")

@handle_errors
    """统一错误处理装饰器, 捕获异常并记录日志后重新抛出"""
    # 用法: @handle_errors
```

### 日志

```python
def init_logging(config: dict[str, Any]) -> None
    """初始化 structlog 日志系统, 配置控制台彩色输出和文件 JSON 轮转"""

def get_logger(name: str | None = None) -> structlog.stdlib.BoundLogger
    """获取 structlog 日志记录器"""
```

